which resulted when Larry and Sergey were
on a road trip without any PR person at all.

00:01:11.730 --> 00:01:15.659
They sat down with me in a conference room
and was telling what this thing is and it

00:01:15.659 --> 00:01:19.139
was one of the very first pieces that kinda
put the stake in the ground that what Google

00:01:19.139 --> 00:01:27.450
was doing was significantly different and
extremely youthful. So, yeah, I've been writing

00:01:27.450 --> 00:01:29.069
about tech for a long time and--

