00:02:02.639 --> 00:02:07.419
which are not fully enough understood, although
I hit on them pretty hard in my book. So,

00:02:07.419 --> 00:02:11.221
its part of the reason, I think, I wrote the
book was to try to emphasize that Facebook

00:02:11.221 --> 00:02:17.720
is a truly unusual company. I would say that
also applies to Google, obviously. But there,

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:24.590
there are many things about Facebook that
even Google doesn't exactly echo, or Facebook

00:02:24.590 --> 00:02:28.519
doesn't echo Google, since Google was the
predecessor.

