close to a million of them were actively protesting

00:04:22.190 --> 00:04:28.750
the introduction of the newsfeed. Now that,
in retrospect, seems kind of odd, considering

00:04:28.750 --> 00:04:34.240
that anyone who uses Facebook knows that the
newsfeed is kind of its central feature without

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:38.000
which it would, more or less, feel pretty
useless.

